TODO Unified templates (syntax, quasiquote, etc)

  If x is a list, then...

  (template (list (~seq 1 ,x) ...))
  =>
  (append-map (lambda (x) (list 1 x)) x)

  (template (syntax a ,x ... c))
  =>
  (syntax-cons a (syntax-append x (syntax c)))

  (template (+ (f ,x) ...))
  =>
  (apply + (map f x))

